oai_dc:dc.dc:title: North Side Public Square, Athens, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the North Side Public Square in Athens, Tennessee. View from image shows a street lined with businesses, and some horse-drawn wagons. Features a divided back and handwritten correspondence on reverse. Postcard printed in Germany. August 25, 1909 postmark.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Utility poles; Electric lines; Telecommunication lines; Carts & wagons; Streets
